{"tid":1088920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【旨意贊助商？】Crossover大陸騷搞新節目 何麗全：製作一定要使錢","createTime":"2019-04-02T11:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T23:24:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb566c707fa0ee00bc5dba8730b96e3e6a7ba847","tid":1088920,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:43:44.000Z","msg":"剛進行裁員不久的亞視（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2UYMdLj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UYMdLj&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m6z4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=8ee4d692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2UYMdLj</a> ），今日在大埔總廠舉行記者會，亞視行政總裁何麗全宣佈大陸節目《VK百男大秀》將與亞視合作，製作新節目，內容是以強調內涵及生活品味的男士為主題。<br />\n何麗全說：「亞視製作香港版《百男大秀》，與亞姐一樣設有大中華及海外賽區，節目形式及製作時間表仍在研究。」對於要撥備投資，何麗全說：「製作一定要使錢，相信能像亞姐一樣吸引廣告商贊助，亞視目前亦有足夠人手應付節目製作，如有需要會增聘人手。」何麗全透露製作部仍有同事上班，娛樂新聞節目如常運作。<br />\n前亞洲先生徐丁及涂諾，早前亦有參與大陸版《百男大秀》拍攝。大陸版拍攝上有不少內褲造型，涂諾表示不介意穿內褲示人，他說：「當年選亞生亦係以內褲取勝。」徐丁表示年紀漸長，穿內褲機會要留給年輕人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190402/large/1554200548_9147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190402%2Flarge%2F1554200548_9147.jpg&h=3d431184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190402/59441872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190402%2F59441872&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m6z4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=952d95cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190402%2F59441872&h=0df3fe84\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190402/59441872</a>"},{"pid":"3cd8a487687f40127451ec2477e15ddab38623b6","tid":1088920,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T23:24:27.000Z","msg":"推"}]}